race.description: First National Real Estate Murray Bridge Stake Pr2
race.comment: STARLIGHT RIOT (8) is a promising dog in the frame at zero of eight starts including six wins and was a last start winner (19.47) over 342m at Angle Park. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. YOU AIN'T IT (7) missed the frame last time at Angle Park but the start prior rocketed around 400m at Gawler in 22.82. Has the ability and can find winning form again. SPECKED (1) has recorded back to back wins, last time scoring at this track over 300m by 5 lengths (16.52). Sure to be thereabouts. FINNISS HONOUR (5) is always a threat when he races at this journey.
